<!doctype html>
<html class="no-js" lang="en" dir="ltr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Robotics | Plinth'17</title>
        <script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/8720ae4a19.js"></script>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/foundation/6.2.3/foundation.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/competitions.css" />
    </head>
    <body>

        <% include partials/header %>
        <%if (!isLoggedIn) { %>
                <% include partials/reg-form %>
        <% } %>

        <div class="content">
            <a href="/competitions"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-left fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
            <div class="row head">
                <div class="small-10 small-centered columns text-center">
                    <h4>Robotics</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row desc">
                <div class="small-12 columns text-center">
                    <p>Robots are fun to play with; robots are even much more fun to build. Robotics is forming a productive tomorrow. Now it’s your chance to be a part of it. While in the race to create the smartest and the most intelligent robots, let’s relive the days of the rise of machines.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="big-wrapper">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="large-8 large-centered small-10 small-centered columns">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="small-10 medium-4 large-4 small-centered medium-uncentered columns">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                                <img src="media/icons/robotics/lfr.svg" class="event-main-page-image" />
                                <div class="container">
                                    <p class="name">LFR</p>
                                    <p class="name-desc">An Autonomous bot that follows black line on white surface or vice-versa.</p>
                                </div>
                                <a href="/competitions/robotics/lfr" class="know-more">Know More ></a>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="small-10 medium-4 large-4 small-centered medium-uncentered columns">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                              <img src="media/icons/robotics/quadcopter.svg" class="event-main-page-image"/>
                              <div class="container">
                                <p class="name">Quadcopter</p>
                                <p class="name-desc">Design a wireless remote controlled flying platform and beat obstacles.</p>
                              </div>
                              <a href="/competitions/robotics/quadcopter" class="know-more">Know More ></a>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="small-10 medium-4 large-4 small-centered medium-uncentered columns">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                              <img src="media/icons/robotics/transporter.svg" class="event-main-page-image" />
                              <div class="container">
                                  <p class="name">Transporter</p>
                                  <p class="name-desc">Build a robot that is capable of picking up and depositing blocks.</p>
                              </div>
                              <a href="/competitions/robotics/transporter" class="know-more">Know More ></a>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="small-10 medium-4 large-4 small-centered medium-uncentered columns">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                              <img src="media/icons/robotics/roborace.svg" class="event-main-page-image" />
                              <div class="container">
                                  <p class="name">Roborace</p>
                                  <p class="name-desc">Construct a remote controlled  robot which can run fast and evade obstacles.</p>
                                  <a href="/competitions/robotics/roborace" class="know-more">Know More ></a>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="small-10 medium-4 large-4 small-centered medium-uncentered columns">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                              <img src="media/icons/robotics/robowar.svg" class="event-main-page-image" />
                              <div class="container">
                                      <p class="name">Robowar</p>
                                      <p class="name-desc">Test your Robot against another in a field of combat.</p>
                              </div>
                              <a href="/competitions/robotics/robowar" class="know-more">Know More ></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small-10 medium-4 large-4 end end small-offset-1 medium-uncentered columns small-1-offset">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                              <img src="media/icons/robotics/robosoccer.svg" class="event-main-page-image" />
                              <div class="container">
                                  <p class="name">Robosoccer</p>
                                  <p class="name-desc">Build bots capable of playing soccer on a robo-soccer arena.</p>
                              </div>
                              <a href="/competitions/robotics/robosoccer" class="know-more">Know More ></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <% include partials/footer %>

    </body>
</html>
